{"tid":144854,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《南華早報》消息：習近平7月訪港","createTime":"2017-03-05T18:32:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-09T01:35:06.000Z","uid":5195,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c6470acdb8bca00aa88a677c674f0b24ed0a0803","tid":144854,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T18:32:49.000Z","msg":"英文《南華早報》引述消息報道，身兼中央軍委主席的國家主席習近平，可能在香港回歸20周年期間，前往香港檢閱解放軍駐港部隊。報道引述解放軍駐港部隊前司令員張仕波的消息表示，檢閱駐港部隊是一種常規做法，但是中央軍委目前仍未作出最終決定。報道又引述張仕波透露，駐港部隊所有前司令員，都獲邀在香港回歸20周年時訪港。<br />\n<br />\n張仕波在2007年12月至2012年10月期間，擔任駐港部隊司令員。前國家主席胡錦濤，曾經在2007年和2012年先後訪港，分別視察過駐港部隊的石崗及昂船洲軍營。"},{"pid":"81e58022ed6315b8db2a2239147d7c9d84cbed66","tid":144854,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T18:50:19.000Z","msg":"終於肯落下一步棋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"086a32e37a52efd5d5fd1db35413d37e787598b5","tid":144854,"uid":14623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T19:26:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇人想見到佢"},{"pid":"0fddad071bcc856f65163f2625297ff0cc44e303","tid":144854,"uid":50018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T19:34:22.000Z","msg":"Time for assassination<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af8ca08d9bd35e190703228584844fe755b29512","tid":144854,"uid":59695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T19:36:29.000Z","msg":"落黎中途被人暗殺就好睇"},{"pid":"cb3b9f13e83bae984bb06919ac38d6bf42c05700","tid":144854,"uid":60794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T19:39:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Time for assassination<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n頭盔都唔戴<img s